{"tid":1085193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【被迫做假】不交就業證明無法畢業 內地大學生統計灌水","createTime":"2019-03-31T04:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T00:02:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5a810e42912b8005fe5508a3ccfd0c852fe2c0","tid":1085193,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"國務院總理李克強在今年的政府工作報告，提出「施政六穩」目標，第一項就是要「穩就業」。今年內地預計有834萬名大學畢業生，創歷史新高，有大學為要向當局展示高就業率，竟要求學生在畢業前，預先提交就業證明，否則會扣起畢業證書，有學生為求拿到證書，被迫提交假的證明。<br />\n內地媒體近年公佈的大學生畢業的就業數字，大多數學校的就業率都超過九成，引來各界質疑這些統計被嚴重灌水。共青團在官方微信指出，有廣東的大學要求畢業生，在5月底前提交就業協議書、就業推薦表、高等學校畢業生登記表等3份就業相關的文件，否則就無法拿到畢業證書。<br />\n報道引述一名姓肖姓大學生表示，有很多同學都未找到工作，只能購買假的證明，以求過關，另一名姓王的學生則指出，有學校甚至會為學生找工作，與企業簽訂就業協議，防止學校就業率數字不好看，但這些協議，給學生的薪金則是特別低。<br />\n人力資源和社會保障部指出，對於學校的違法違規事件，近期有增加的趨勢，即日起至下月26日展開清理整頓專項執法行動。官員更重申，教育部早在2016年已經發佈通知，禁止大學以任何方式，強迫畢業生簽訂就業協議和勞動合約，或將畢業證書、學位證書發放與簽約掛鈎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190330/large/1553940780_f2c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190330%2Flarge%2F1553940780_f2c8.jpg&h=3dcc7cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190330/59430897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190330%2F59430897&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9xckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=043e4234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190330%2F59430897&h=e38e3f3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190330/59430897</a>"},{"pid":"9786c2874e9c00671f9d4e80be1a66190fea513d","tid":1085193,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c5ed3d11e1e3ca792c29532df3635981697a71e","tid":1085193,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:41:29.000Z","msg":"偷呃拐騙<br />\n啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282505fa9b99ca211109282df98cf683b2d30815","tid":1085193,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:44:00.000Z","msg":"支那又係到造數據"},{"pid":"3d02d3dfec27d157b569e439e30ce8895a5acf96","tid":1085193,"uid":120814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:45:08.000Z","msg":"只有支那, 沒有內地"},{"pid":"7bc8a5f63d2de1e39c0d34d8a95928783fe95325","tid":1085193,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d02d3dfec27d157b569e439e30ce8895a5acf96","tid":1085193,"uid":120814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:45:08.000Z","msg":"只有支那, 沒有內地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:53:58.000Z","msg":"內國 咁香港就外國"},{"pid":"b1fdbfb8bfa95e9fd660e95aa00d7cdcb767685d","tid":1085193,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc8a5f63d2de1e39c0d34d8a95928783fe95325","tid":1085193,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d02d3dfec27d157b569e439e30ce8895a5acf96","tid":1085193,"uid":120814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:45:08.000Z","msg":"只有支那, 沒有內地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:53:58.000Z","msg":"內國 咁香港就外國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:17:09.000Z","msg":"係其他國家"},{"pid":"ecf13876358ed6efbe3b16793f708c7c8cedf639","tid":1085193,"uid":139473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:02:26.000Z","msg":"對上幾年都講大陸大學生搵唔到野/難搵野做<br />\n出埋仆街政策呃人大學生就業率高"}]}